data.description: Turnkey duplex with proven rental history and low maintenance! Built in 2020. No CDD or HOA. The upstairs unit is a 2 bed 2 bath. Downstairs unit is a 1 bedroom 1 bath. Both units have luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the common areas and granite countertops with stainless steel appliances. Each unit also has its own laundry connections. Both units are currently occupied with a combined rental income of $3100.00, monthly.
